{
  "stem": "16395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was 80 kilometers from the town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I came in and my brother was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was my niece, the one what she is alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She and the old lady, the grandmother, because the little girl-- they had a little girl from two years old-- and they didn't think that she should go out in the middle of the town so they hide it in the attic and the Germans never came up and they survived.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The grandmother was my grandmother and his grandmother, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, his wife's grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was maybe, I would say, 85 years old or 83 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe not even that because my mother married when she was 15, and she was her first child.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was in the 80s, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came home and my brother was alive, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For some reason, he escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't jump the train, but he escaped and he was alive with his wife and the two children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't go down, either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were hidden where they lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I lived in that my brother-in-law because he had my-- he had a daughter and a small child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We lived in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was well off because he worked for the Germans and the Germans gave him some bread, and he used to bring it to us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we didn't trust the Germans, so we knew we had to make a hiding place for ourselves and with did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The place where we-- this was already in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And since he was a builder before the war, he was making wagons, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he knew very well how to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
